ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
If(
    !IsBlank(BuildingDropdown.SelectedText) && BuildingDropdown.SelectedText.street_full <> buildingDefaultText && !IsBlank(FloorDropdown.SelectedText) && FloorDropdown.SelectedText.floor_name <> floorDefaultText && !IsBlank(NeighbourhoodDropdown.SelectedText) && NeighbourhoodDropdown.SelectedText.name <> neighbourhoodDefaultText && !IsBlank(SeatingTypeDropdown.SelectedText) && SeatingTypeDropdown.SelectedText.seating_type <> seatingTypeDefaultText && !IsBlank(DatePicker.SelectedDate) && locDateError = "None" && !IsBlank(TimeRangeDropdown.SelectedText),
    DisplayMode.Edit,
    DisplayMode.Disabled
)

[
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.sunday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.monday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.tuesday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.wednesday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.thursday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.friday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text),
    LookUp(colTranslationTable, key = "datepicker.shortdays.saturday" && language.Value = gblAppUserLang, text)
]
